- MT1      : Total cross section                                  1031 1451
                                                                  1031 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range,    1031 1451
or partly reproduced using experimental data.                     1031 1451
                                                                  1031 1451
- MT2      : Elastic scattering cross section                     1031 1451
                                                                  1031 1451
Obtained by subtracting the non-elastic cross section from the    1031 1451
total cross section.                                              1031 1451
                                                                  1031 1451
